Package ohos.ai.cv.common

Class ParamKey

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.ai.cv.common.ParamKey
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DocRefineParamKey, SrParamKey, TextParamKey

    public class ParamKey
extends Object
    Provides keys passed to PacMap.

    This class defines public keys passed to PacMap in the CV engine for data communication with external modules.

    Since:
    1
